docs/superpowers/plans/2026-04-10-admin-controls.md:1302:Full redesign. Layout A: single scroll. Order: header → stat bar → system controls → error banner → Add User → user cards → model profiles (collapsible). User cards get an inline block control section. All features (block, force-logout, kill job, rate override) accessible from each user card.
